\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
In the above distributions, 
\begin_inset Formula $MN$
\end_inset

 is the multi-variate normal distribution, 
\begin_inset Formula $Bern$
\end_inset

 is the Bernoulli distribution, 
\begin_inset Formula $Beta$
\end_inset

